swer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<p>The AUM, short for\n          <a\n            href=https://groww.in/p/asset-under-management/\n            class=\"bodyLargeHeavy schemeFaq15SNextAnchorLink contentAccent\"\n          > Assets Under Management </a>\n        of HDFC Flexi Cap Direct Plan Growth is ₹1,01,821.82Cr as of 13 Jun 2026.</p>"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How to Redeem HDFC Flexi Cap Direct Plan Growth?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<p>If you want to sell your HDFC Flexi Cap Direct Plan Growth holdings, go to your holding on the app or\n        web and simply click on it. You will get two options - redeem & invest more; click on redeem and enter your\n        desired amount or if you wish to redeem the entire holding amount then select the 'redeem all' checkbox.</p>\n        "}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I invest in SIP and Lump Sum of HDFC Flexi Cap Direct Plan Growth?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<p>You can select either\n          <a\n            href= https://groww.in/p/sip-systematic-investment-plan/\n            class=\"bodyLargeHeavy schemeFaq15SNextAnchorLink contentAccent\"\n          > SIP </a> or\n          <a\n            href= https://groww.in/p/lump-sum/\n            class=\"bodyLargeHeavy schemeFaq15SNextAnchorLink contentAccent\"\n          > Lumpsum </a> investment of HDFC Flexi Cap Direct Plan Growth based on\n        your investment objective and risk tolerance.</p>"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the NAV of HDFC Flexi Cap Direct Plan Growth?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<p>The NAV of HDFC Flexi Cap Direct Plan Growth is ₹2,155.38 as of 12 Jun 2026.</p>"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the PE and PB ratio of HDFC Flexi Cap Direct Plan Growth?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<p>The\n          <a\n            href= https://groww.in/p/pe-ratio\n            class=\"bodyLargeHeavy schemeFaq15SNextAnchorLink contentAccent\"\n          > PE ratio </a>ratio of HDFC Flexi 